===Adjective===
'''Rumsfeldian'''

# Of or pertaining to ''[[Wikipedia:Donald Rumsfeld|Donald Rumsfeld]]'' or policies associated with him.
#:''{{{2|The Rumsfeldian theory of war relies heavily on technology}}}'' Mir Bahmanyar, ''Shadow Warriors''

===Origins===
Although Rumsfeld held numerous prior positions, the term began in [[2001]] and solidified itself with regard to Rumsfeld's management of the Iraq War.

